com.xilinx.rapidwright.rwroute

Class PartialRouter

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.rwroute.RWRoute
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.rwroute.PartialRouter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RapidStreamRoute

    public class PartialRouter
extends RWRoute
    A class extending RWRoute for partial routing. In partial routing mode, nets that are already fully- or partially- routed will be preserved and only the unrouted connections (as specified by the pinsToRoute parameter in the constructor) are tackled. Enabling soft preserve allows preserved routing that may be the cause of any unroutable connections to be ripped up and re-routed.

        Partially routes a Design instance; specifically, all nets with no routing PIPs already present.
        Parameters:
        design - The Design instance to be routed.
        args - An array of string arguments, can be null. If null, the design will be routed in the full timing-driven routing mode with default a RWRouteConfig instance. For more options of the configuration, please refer to the RWRouteConfig class.
        Returns:
        Routed design.

        Partially routes a Design instance; specifically, all nets with no routing PIPs already present.
        Parameters:
        design - The Design instance to be routed.
        args - An array of string arguments, can be null. If null, the design will be routed in the full timing-driven routing mode with default a RWRouteConfig instance. For more options of the configuration, please refer to the RWRouteConfig class.
